item.title: Mobileye IPO to be Market Entry for Self-Driving Tech Firm, Intel CEO Says
item.description: Mobileye IPO to be Market Entry for Self-Driving Tech Firm, Intel CEO Says Intel's initial public offering of its self-driving tech company Mobileye was not a capital raise but part of the company's efforts to make an entry into the market, CEO Pat Gelsinger said on Monday.
